to the regulation.

26:54.709 --> 26:56.770
Obviously, we in California are going to do what's right for us.

26:56.850 --> 27:01.414
We hope that the board will support us as we move forward in doing the right thing as that kind of moves on.

27:02.275 --> 27:07.479
